      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">1.
      </span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">在获取明确同意的情况下转让：获得您的明确同意后，我们会向其他⽅转让您的个⼈信息；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">2.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">在我们平台服务提供者发⽣合并、收购或破产清算情形，或其他涉及合并、收购或破产清算情形
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">时，如涉及到个⼈信息转让，我们会要求新的持有您个⼈信息的公司、组织继续受本政策的约束，否
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">则我们将要求该公司、组织和个⼈重新向您征求授权同意。
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">（三）共享、转让、披露个⼈信息时事先征得授权同意的例外
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">以下情形中，共享、转让、公开披露您的个⼈信息⽆需事先征得您的授权同意：
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">1.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">与我们履⾏法律法规规定的义务相关的；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">2.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">与国家安全、国防安全直接相关的；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">3.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">与公共安全、公共卫⽣、重⼤公共利益直接相关的；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">4.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">与刑事侦查、起诉、审判和判决执⾏等直接相关的；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">5.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">出于维护您或其他个⼈的⽣命、财产等重⼤合法权益但⼜很难得到本⼈同意的；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">6.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">您⾃⾏向社会公众公开的个⼈信息；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">7.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">从合法公开披露的信息中收集个⼈信息的，如合法的新闻报道、政府信息公开等渠道。
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">8.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">根据个⼈信息主体要求签订和履⾏合同所必需的；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">9.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">⽤于维护所提供的产品或服务的安全稳定运⾏所必需的，包括发现、处置产品或服务的故障；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">10.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">法律法规规定的其他情形。
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">根据法律规定，共享、转让经去标识化处理的个⼈信息，且确保数据接收⽅⽆法复原并重新识别个⼈
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">信息主体的，不属于个⼈信息的对外共享、转让及公开披露⾏为，对此类数据的保存及处理将⽆需另
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">⾏向您通知并征得您的同意。
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">如您不同意我们按照上述条款向第三⽅提供您的个⼈信息，请您⽴即停⽌使⽤我们平台服务。
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">四、我们如何保存和保护您的个⼈信息
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">(</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">⼀</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">)</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">我们如何保存您的个⼈信息
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">1.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">存储信息的地点
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">我们遵守法律法规的规定，将境内收集的⽤户个⼈信息存储于境内。
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">2.</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">存储信息的期限
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">⼀般⽽⾔，我们仅为实现⽬的所必需的最短时间保留您的个⼈信息。但在下列情况下，我们有可能因
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Regular;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">需符合法律要求，更改个⼈信息的存储时间：
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">（</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">1</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">）为遵守适⽤的法律法规等有关规定；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">（</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">2</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">）为遵守法院判决、裁定或其他法律程序的规定；
      </span></p>
    <p class="Normal" style="text-align:left;"><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">（</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-fareast-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;mso-bidi-font-family:SFUI-Regular_wdth_opsz110000_GRAD_wght24E0000;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;">3</span><span
        style="color:#454545;font-size:12pt;font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-fareast-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;mso-bidi-font-family:PingFangSC-Semibold;lang:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-ansi-language:X-NONE;font-weight:bold;">）为遵守相关政府机关或法定授权组织的要求；
      </span></p>
